            <div class="ArticleImgContent">
                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/aid/press-centre/press-releases/2010/Agreement-on-economic-stimulus-package-to-reduce-sick-leave-and-new-IA-agreement.html?id=594044" title="">
                        Agreement on economic stimulus package to reduce sick leave and new IA agreement
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[24.02.2010]</p>
                <p>The Government and the employer/employee organisations have agreed on an extensive economic stimulus package to reduce sick leave and a new and more goal-oriented IA agreement. </p>
                
                
                <p>
                    
                    
                </p>
                                 
           </div>
