            <div class="ArticleImgContent">
                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/aid/press-centre/press-releases/2010/Norwegian-wage-settlements-in-2010.html?id=593799" title="">
                        Norwegian wage settlements in 2010
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[19.02.2010]</p>
                <p>The Norwegian Technical Calculation Committee for Wage Settlements presents the preliminary report on the basis for wage settlements in 2010.</p>
                
                
                <p>
                    
                    
                </p>
                                 
