            </a>
            <div class="ArticleImgContent">
                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/aid/press-centre/press-releases/2010/expert-group-suggests-additional-measure.html?id=592680" title="">
                        Expert group suggests additional measures to reduce sick leave
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[03.02.2010]</p>
                <p>The government received suggestions today from the expert group that has considered measures that could reduce sick leave. The group proposes a main strategy for the future that prioritises active participation measures, return-to-work strategies and graduated sick leave.</p>
                
                
