            <div class="ArticleImgContent">
                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/aid/press-centre/press-releases/2007/United-Nations-adopts-Declaration-on-Rig.html?id=480895" title="">
                        United Nations adopts Declaration on Rights of Indigenous Peoples
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[13.09.2007]</p>
                <p>– This is a historic day for the Sami population and other indigenous peoples across the world, says the Minister of Labour and Social Inclusion, Mr. Bjarne Håkon Hanssen.</p>
                
                
                <p>
                    
                    
                </p>
                                 
